prompt.title: Embedding for AI-Native Apps: Intuitive User-Centric Development
prompt.content: AI-Native Applications focus on human-understandable concepts such as personas, knowledge, and actions, rather than traditional programming elements like if statements, loops, variables, or tokens. This paradigm shift aims to make application development more intuitive and user-centric.
